# Web3Forms access key — submissions from the booking modal post here and
# Web3Forms emails them to the address you registered.
#
# Get your key (free, no signup beyond email verification):
#   https://web3forms.com/
#
# Steps:
#   1. Visit https://web3forms.com/
#   2. Enter your email address (franciscorobalino1991@gmail.com)
#   3. Check your inbox for the access key
#   4. Copy this file to `.env` and paste your key below
#   5. Restart `npm run dev` so Vite picks up the new env var
#
# The key is safe to expose in client code — Web3Forms validates the
# request origin (configurable in their dashboard) and runs spam filtering.
VITE_WEB3FORMS_KEY=
